Write a Python program that accepts a word from the user and reverse it.

Sample Test Case

Input : Edyoda

output: adoydE

######################    CODE STARTS FROM HERE!

word = input('hey user! Give me a word and watch a magic : ') #Edyoda
        #we have a string

print(word[::-1]) 
# print(list[a:b:c]) will include characters from a to b (excluding b) with the difference of c between them 
# and if c is negative it just mean in reverse order

